Class CardStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.payu.india.Model.CardStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class CardStatus
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Created by franklin on 7/2/15. simple bean implementation of card status. it holds the issuing bank's up/down status. To avail this facility app should make an api using ValueAddedServiceTask app will get response at PayuResponse.issuingBankStatus TODO assign values for the following in PayuConstants UP Down Partial down.
